In Part One we looked at the history of relations between Britain

00:00:33.029 --> 00:00:38.569
and Europe, from the Romans invading in 55BC right up to the UK’s

00:00:38.609 --> 00:00:43.579
decision to break with the European Union, over 2,000 years later.

